Package org.biojava.bio

Class AnnotationChanger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biojava.utils.AbstractChangeable
      • org.biojava.bio.AbstractAnnotation
        • org.biojava.bio.AnnotationChanger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Annotation, Changeable
    public class AnnotationChanger
extends AbstractAnnotation
    AnnotationChanger remaps the values of an Annotation to new values specified by a ValueChanger. This will modify the values associated with properties, but not the property names. For writing light-weigth adaptors to project one type of Annotation to another using a ChangeTable.
    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    Matthew Pocock
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
